e new ruling, trading Bitcoin is now legalized in the country.<br/><br/>Despite the formal recognition given to Bitcoin as a commodity, the ban on cryptocurrency payment is still in effect, as the Indonesian regulator said their “mandate is the protection of Rupiah sovereignty and monopoly within the country.”</div><div class='itemTags'>Tags:&nbsp;bitcoin, news</div><div class='source'>Source:&nbsp;<a href="https://www.hukumonline.com/berita/baca/lt5c63e9b29ebf4/bitcoin-cs-sah-diperdagangkan-di-bursa-komoditi--bagaimana-isi-aturannya" >https://www.hukumonline.com/berita/baca/lt5c63e9b29ebf4/bitcoin-cs-sah-diperdagangkan-di-bursa-komoditi--bagaimana-isi-aturannya</a></div><div class='socialButtons'><span class='st_facebook_hcount' displayText='Facebook'></span><span class='st_twitter_hcount' displayText='Tweet'></span><span class='st_linkedin_hcount' displayText='LinkedIn'></span><span class='st_googleplus_hcount' displayText='Google +'></span><span class='st_whatsapp_hcount' displayText='WhatsApp'></span><span class='st_reddit_hcount' displayText='Reddit'></span></div><script src='https://ws.sharethis.com/button/buttons.js' type='text/javascript'></script><script type='text/javascript'>stLight.options({publisher: "d0147334-a21b-4b80-a4a4-65d610434a53", doNotHash: false, doNotCopy: false, hashAddressBar: false});</script></div></div><footer><div class='about'><a href="/about">About</a></div><div class='copyright'><span>&#169;</span><span>Hodlex Ltd © 2016-2018</span></div></footer></div><script>
